eadword":"soliloquy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 自言自语(the act of talking to oneself); 戏剧独白(a dramatic monologue that"},{"type":"text","text":"[sa'lrlakwi]"},{"type":"text","text":"represents a series of unspoken reflections)"},{"type":"entry","text":"gibe","headword":"gibe"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.嘟弄，讥笑（to jeer or taunt;scoff）n.嘲笑，讥笑"},{"type":"text","text":"[d3arb]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：也写作jibe，但jibe还有另一个意思“与一致”，是GRE常考的"},{"type":"text","text":"释义。"},{"type":"entry","text":"harass","headword":"harass"},{"type":"text","text":".侵扰，烦扰(to annoy persistently)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ha'raes]"},{"type":"text","text":"harass theborder area窜扰边境"},{"type":"entry","text":"incandescent","headword":"incandescent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 遇热发光的，发白热光的(white, glowing, or luminous with intense heat)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,inkaen'desnt]"},{"type":"entry","text":"fussy","headword":"fussy"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 爱挑剔的，难取悦的(overly exacting and hard to please)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fAsi]"},{"type":"text","text":"dainty, exacting, fastidious, finicky, meticulous"},{"type":"entry","text":"carve","headword":"carve"},{"type":"text","text":".雕刻(to shape by cutting, chipping and hewing); (把肉等)切成片(to slice)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka:rv]"},{"type":"text","text":"cleave, dissect, dissever, sever, splt"},{"type":"entry","text":"desultory","headword":"desultory"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不连贯的（disconnected)：散漫的(not methodical;random）"},{"type":"text","text":"['desalto:ri]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（向下）+sult（跳）+ory→跳来跳去→散漫的"},{"type":"entry","text":"quash","headword":"quash"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 镇压(to suppress); (依法)取消(to nullify by judicial action)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kwo:]"},{"type":"text","text":"abrogate, repeal, rescind"},{"type":"entry","text":"elude","headword":"elude"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.逃避（to avoid adroitly)：搞不清，理解不了（to escape the perception or"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'lu:d]"},{"type":"text","text":"understanding)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：e（向外）+lud（玩）+e→想出去玩→逃避"},{"type":"text","text":"eschew, evade, shun"},{"type":"entry","text":"sabotage","headword":"sabotage"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.阴谋破坏，颠覆活动（deliberate subversion）"},{"type":"text","text":"['saebata:3]"},{"type":"text","text":"anact of military sabotage军事破坏活动"},{"type":"entry","text":"drab","headword":"drab"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 黄褐色的(of a dull yellowish brown);单调的，泛味的(not bright or lively;"},{"type":"text","text":"[draeb]"},{"type":"text","text":"monotonous)"}]},{"number":283,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱L序版"},{"type":"text","text":"Thomas Paine, whose political writing was often flamboyant, was in private"},{"type":"text","text":"life a surprisingly simple man: he lived in rented rooms, ate little, and wore crab"},{"type":"text","text":"clothes."},{"type":"entry","text":"congruous","headword":"congruous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.—致的，符合的(being in agreement, harmony, or correspondence);[数]全"},{"type":"text","text":"['kongru:as]"},{"type":"text","text":"等的"},{"type":"entry","text":"gall","headword":"gall"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 胆汁(bile);忽恨(hatred; bitter feeling)"},{"type":"text","text":"[g>:1]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈联想记忆：监狱的高墙（wall诉说着怨恨（gall)"},{"type":"entry","text":"frail","headword":"frail"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.脆弱的(fragile, delicate);不坚实的(slender and delicate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[frerl]"},{"type":"text","text":"园可能是fragile（adj易碎的）的变体"},{"type":"definition","text":"A human being is quite a frail creature, for the gloss of rationality that covers"},{"type":"text","text":"his or her fears and insecurity is thin and often easily breached."},{"type":"text","text":"feeble, flimsy"},{"type":"entry","text":"prohibitive","headword":"prohibitive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.禁止的，抑制的(tending to prohibit or restrain);贵得买不起的（so high or"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'hrbativ]"},{"type":"text","text":"burdensome as to discourage purchase or use)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pro（提前）+hibit（拿住）+ive（的）→提前拿住的→禁止的，抑制的"},{"type":"entry","text":"resent","headword":"resent"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 增恶, 忽恨(to feel or express annoyance or ill will)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'zent]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：re（反）+sent（感情）→反感→增恶"},{"type":"text","text":"I Was he so thin-skinned, then, to resent any small jest at his expense?"},{"type":"entry","text":"conflate","headword":"conflate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 合并(to combine or mix)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kan'flert]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：con（共同）+flat（吹气）+e→吹到一起→合并"},{"type":"entry","text":"misanthrope","headword":"misanthrope"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 厌恶人类者(a person who hates humankind)"},{"type":"text","text":"['mrsanθraup]"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：mis（恨）+anthrop（人类）+e→恨人类的人→厌恶人类者"},{"type":"text","text":"Because he was a misanthrope, he shunned human society."},{"type":"entry","text":"subsidize","headword":"subsidize"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 津贴，资助(to furnish with a subsidy)"},{"type":"text","text":"['sAbsidarz]"},{"type":"text","text":"finance, fund, sponsor"},{"type":"entry","text":"impersonal","headword":"impersonal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不受个人感情影响的(having no personal reference or connection)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rm'ps:rsanl]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：im（不）+personalk个人的）→不投入个人感情的→不受个人感情影响的"},{"type":"entry","text":"rage","headword":"rage"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.盛怒(violent and uncontrolled anger) v 狂怒，大发雷置(to be in a rage)"}]},{"number":284,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 24 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"decrepit","headword":"decrepit"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 衰老的, 破|旧的(broken down or worn out by old age,illness, or long use)"},{"type":"text","text":"[di'kreprt]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：de（加强）+crepit（破裂声）→破旧得一碰就裂→破l旧的"},{"type":"entry","text":"incumbent","headword":"incumbent"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.在职者，现任者（the holder of an office or benefice)adj义不容辞的（obligatory)"},{"type":"text","text":"[n'kAmbant]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：in+cumb（躺）+ent→躺在（职位）上的人→在职者"},{"type":"entry","text":"exorbitant","headword":"exorbitant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.过分的，过度的(exceeding the bounds of custom, propriety, or reason)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1g'zo:rbrtant]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（出）+orbit（轨道）+ant→出轨的→过分的"},{"type":"text","text":"exorbitantfees过度收费"},{"type":"text","text":"excessive, extravagant, extreme, immoderate, inordinate"},{"type":"entry","text":"overstate","headword":"overstate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.弯张，对-言过其实（toexaggerate）"},{"type":"text","text":"[auvar'stert]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：over（过分）+state（陈述）夸张"},{"type":"entry","text":"grave","headword":"grave"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.严肃的，庄重的（serious)n.墓穴"},{"type":"text","text":"[grerv]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：grav（重）+e→庄重的"},{"type":"entry","text":"transgress","headword":"transgress"},{"type":"definition","text":"v冒犯，违背(to go beyond limits prescribed by; violate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[traenz'gres]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：trans（横向）+gress（走）→横着走→冒犯"},{"type":"entry","text":"dupe","headword":"dupe"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 易上当者(a person easily tricked or fooled)"},{"type":"text","text":"[du:p]"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.丰满的(having a full rounded usually pleasing form） v.使丰满，使变图(to"},{"type":"entry","text":"plump","headword":"plump"},{"type":"text","text":"[plAmp]"},{"type":"text","text":"make well-rounded or full in form)"},{"type":"entry","text":"remiss","headword":"remiss"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 疏忽的, 不留心的(negligent in the performance of work or duty)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'mis]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（一再）+miss（放）→一再放掉→疏忽的"},{"type":"entry","text":"grudge","headword":"grudge"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.吝借，勉强给或承认(to be reluctant to give or admit);"},{"type":"text","text":"[grAd3]"},{"type":"text","text":"不满，忽恨(to feel resentful about sth.)"