","text":"adj.无数的，数不清的（too great or numerous to count)"},{"type":"text","text":"[An'tauld]"},{"type":"entry","text":"stereotype","headword":"stereotype"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.固定形式，老套(sth. conforming to a fixed or general pattern)"},{"type":"text","text":"['steriatarp]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：stereo（立体）+type（形状）→固定形式"},{"type":"entry","text":"impressionable","headword":"impressionable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 易受影响的(easily affected by impressions)"},{"type":"text","text":"[xm'pre{anabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"We realized that John was still young and impressionable, but were"},{"type":"text","text":"nevertheless surprised at his naivete."},{"type":"entry","text":"voluptuous","headword":"voluptuous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 撩人的(suggesting sensual pleasure)：沉溺酒色的(abandoned to enjoyments"},{"type":"text","text":"[va'lAptfuas]"},{"type":"text","text":"of luxury, pleasure, or sensual gratification)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：volupt（享乐，快感）+uous→沉溺酒色的"},{"type":"entry","text":"ductile","headword":"ductile"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 易延展的(capable of being stretched); 可塑的(easily molded; pliable)"},{"type":"text","text":"[daktarl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：duct（引导）+ile→易引导的→可塑的"},{"type":"entry","text":"restitution","headword":"restitution"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 归还(a restoration to its rightful owner); 赔偿(giving an equivalent for some"},{"type":"text","text":"[restr'tu:{n]"},{"type":"text","text":"injury)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：re（重新）+stitut（站立）+ion→重新站过去→归还"},{"type":"entry","text":"stratagem","headword":"stratagem"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.谋略，策略(a cleverly contrived trick or scheme)"},{"type":"text","text":"['straetadzam]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：strata（层次）+gem→有层次的计划→谋略"},{"type":"text","text":"That the Third Battalion's fifty-percent casualty rate transformed its assault on"},{"type":"text","text":"Hill 306 from a brilliant stratagem into a debacle does not gainsay eyewitness"},{"type":"exa